info.description: # Welcome to the Centerpoint API! ### Type Rest/JSON ### Pattern: JSONAPI 1.0 [https://jsonapi.org/format/1.0/](https://jsonapi.org/format/1.0/) ### Authorization To authenticate you API calls, add the `Authorization` header to all requests. The value of this header is your API Token from the developer portal. ### Developer Portal [https://api-portal.centerpointconnect.io](https://api-portal.centerpointconnect.io) ### Data Heirarchy - The data Heirarchy starts with Companies. - Under each Company lives one or more Properties. - On each Property lives your Service Work Orders, Opportunities, Production Jobs. - All three of these are retrieved from the Productions endpoint. - On each Production lives Invoices, Materials Used, Purchase Orders, Service Time, etc. - Contacts live under Companies, but can be applied to specific Properties and Productions.
info.title: Centerpoint Connect API
